Copyright (c) 2026 SNU Connectome Lab, Seoul National University

This repository contains a pipeline for curating naturalistic fMRI literature
and running NotebookLM-based wisdom synthesis queries. The license below applies
to the **code** (Python scripts, shell scripts, Makefile, documentation).

Third-party content:
- PDFs (not included in repo — see .gitignore): copyright of respective publishers
- Paper metadata (papers_all.json, etc.): derived from public PubMed records
- Query responses (answers/*.md): generated by Google NotebookLM,
  licensed under the CC BY-SA 4.0 attribution requirement with preserved citations

